    "For I > I max, we keep Φ(i) = 1 capturing full automation.",
    "Bout of Automation (Mixed Distribution) We consider a fourth scenario in which rapid advances in AI automate a large fraction of tasks within a short time span, but in which we assume that there remains an unbounded tail of tasks that cannot be automated, for example, because of legal or cultural reasons.",
